<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5> lay a weight on something • lay weight on something</xh5><p> <i>lay a weight on something</i>—(also: put a weight on something) add weight to smth.; make smth. heavy: Try either bending a warm board carefully by hand, or <u>lay a weight on</u> it overnight.</p><p><i>lay weight on something—</i>emphasize smth.; treat smth. as being particularly important: We have <u>laid weight on</u> the problem of quality ever since the company’s inception.</p></entry>
